%2FChangeLog", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/gcc%2Ftestsuite%2FChangeLog?ref=17bbca74807b33cbebdea7761536468e147cf197", "patch": "@@ -1,3 +1,8 @@\n+2006-06-23  Steven G. Kargl  <kargls@comcast.net>\n+\n+\tPR fortran/27981\n+\t* gfortran.dg/simpleif_2.f90: New test.\n+\n 2006-06-23  Lee Millward  <lee.millward@gmail.com>\n \n \t* g++.dg/template/error22.C: Fix typo."}, {"sha": "0d8e6dda966831568736a6da51fd19856c968bc3", "filename": "gcc/testsuite/gfortran.dg/simpleif_2.f90", "status": "added", "additions": 7, "deletions": 0, "changes": 7, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/17bbca74807b33cbebdea7761536468e147cf197/gcc%2Ftestsuite%2Fgfortran.dg%2Fsimpleif_2.f90", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/17bbca74807b33cbebdea7761536468e147cf197/gcc%2Ftestsuite%2Fgfortran.dg%2Fsimpleif_2.f90", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/gcc%2Ftestsuite%2Fgfortran.dg%2Fsimpleif_2.f90?ref=17bbca74807b33cbebdea7761536468e147cf197", "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,7 @@\n+! { dg-do compile }\n+! PR 27981\n+program a\n+   real x\n+   real, pointer :: y\n+   if (.true.) x = 12345678901 ! { dg-error \"Integer too big\" }\n+end program a"}]}